  <h1>Cheese Chompers 3D - Game Summary</h1>
  <p><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://colorrush.org/cheese-chompers-3d" target="_blank">https://colorrush.org/cheese-chompers-3d</a></p>

  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>
    Cheese Chompers 3D is a fast-paced, browser-based arena game developed in Unity, where players take control of bouncy, unpredictable rats competing in chaotic showdowns. 
    With vivid 3D visuals, dynamic physics, and explosive knockouts, this rodent brawler delivers a wildly entertaining experience. 
    Whether going head-to-head with AI or real players, every match is packed with hilarity and surprise.
  </p>

  <h2>Gameplay Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Battle in a single vibrant 3D arena filled with energetic and unpredictable rat interactions</li>
    <li>Control expressive 3D rats with exaggerated, comical animations</li>
    <li>Knock out opponents with forceful hits and enjoy flashy explosion effects</li>
    <li>Use mid-air flips for a burst of speed—ideal for surprise attacks or quick escapes</li>
    <li>Enjoy lively visuals and sound design that enhance the game’s playful tone</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Objectives</h2>
  <p>
    The goal is simple: <strong>be the last rat standing</strong>. Outsmart and outmaneuver your opponents using movement, momentum, and perfectly timed flips 
    to launch them out of the arena before they get the best of you.
  </p>

  <h2>How to Play</h2>
  <p>
    Navigate your rat with intuitive WASD controls, leap into the air using Space, and use momentum to push rivals off the edge. 
    With no scores or timers to worry about, it's all about staying in the game and creating chaos.
  </p>

  <h2>Physics-Based Fun</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Collisions are bouncy and unpredictable, making every encounter unique</li>
    <li>Faster movement results in more powerful impacts, rewarding speed and precision</li>
    <li>Edges are dangerous—just one bump can send you flying</li>
    <li>Chain reactions from one hit can take out multiple opponents</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Controls</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>WASD</strong> – Move your rat</li>
    <li><strong>Space</strong> – Jump and flip for a speed boost</li>
    <li><strong>Mouse</strong> – Adjust the camera angle</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Ready to Chomp?</h2>
  <p>
    Jump into the absurd world of Cheese Chompers 3D and prove yourself as the ultimate rodent warrior. 
    Flip, bash, and bounce your way to victory!
  </p>

